arChildNodes.szComment: The ghost boy speaks with child-like sadness and a damning calmness.

The tired old man goes into a fit of fear as his son manifests again. This CAN'T BE HAPPENING type moment. He's remourseful and fearful of what this ghost wants. His conscience is dirty with his sons imprissonment.
The old mans fear climaxes as he attempts to place false blame on the ghost of his son. He's unable to finish his statement, too weak to rebuff the spirit standing before him.
The old man is terrified of what he will find at the asylum
